quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  2,203,aur ( qiyam money ke ) dinon mein ( jo ) ginti ke ( din mein ) khuda ko yaad karo. agar koi jaldi kere ( aur ) do hi din mein ( chal day ) to is par bhi kuch gunah nahi. aur jo baad taq thehra rahay is par bhi kuch gunah nahi. yeh baatein is shakhs ke liye hain jo ( khuda se ) daray aur tum log khuda se drtay raho aur jaan rakho ke tum sab is ke paas jama kiye jao ge .
  2,204,aur koi shakhs to aisa hai jis ki guftagu duniya ki zindagi mein tum ko dilkash maloom hoti hai aur woh apni maani alzhaimer par khuda ko gawah banata hai halaank woh sakht jhagralu hai
  2,205,aur jab peeth phair kar chala jata hai to zameen mein dorta phirta hai taakay is mein fitnah angazi kere aur khaiti ko ( barbaad ) aur ( insanon aur hewanon ki ) nasal ko nabood kardey aur khuda fitnah angazi ko pasand nahi karta
  2,206,aur jab is se kaha jata hai ke khuda se khauf kar to ghuroor is ko gunah mein phansa deta hai. so aisay ko jahannum sazawar hai. aur woh bohat bura thikana hai
  2,207,aur koi shakhs aisa hai ke khuda ki khushnodi haasil karne ke liye apni jaan beech dalta hai aur khuda bundon par bohat meharban hai
  2,208,momino! islam mein poooray poooray daakhil hojao aur shetan ke peechay nah chalo woh to tumhara Sarih dushman hai
  2,209,phir agar tum ehkaam roshan poanch jaane ke baad larkharajao to jaan jao ke khuda ghalib ( aur ) hikmat wala hai
  2,210,kiya yeh log isi baat ke munhtazir hain ke un par khuda ( ka azaab ) baadal ke saybanon mein aa nazil ho aur farishtay bhi ( utar ayen ) aur kaam tamam kardiya jaye aur sab kamon ka rujoo khuda hi ki taraf hai
